data.description: Incredible piece of property located on 2 gorgeous acres! Wanting space both inside and outside? You have found it here. Home features lots of space and rooms but no doubt the most impressive room is the oversized kitchen. Whether you are cooking for just the family or a large group you will love all the room and layout it provides. When you are done enjoying dinner, take a walk outside around your FLAT yard. Beautiful hardwood trees throughout and 2 mostly flat acres surround the house. Then take a break and relax in the gazebo and enjoy the surroundings. Properties like this are becoming harder to find. Call now!
